    {
      "instruction": "<p>Bash your <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>breast</strong> <strong>portion[s]</strong> with a <strong>rolling</strong> <strong>pin</strong> until evenly flattened – these are your <strong>chicken escalopes</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chicken escalopes</strong> to a bowl with your<strong> five-spice mix </strong>and <strong>cornflour</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the chicken is fully coated in the cornflour mixture – this is your <strong>five-spice coated chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
