            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Once the chips have been in the oven for 25 min, move them to one side of the tray[s] and add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to the other side</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for a final 4-5 min or until the brioche buns are lightly toasted and the chips are golden and crispy</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
